<AbstractNarration>Abstract&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Under this award the PI will study the Amsterdam and St. Paul hotspots in the Indian Ocean as a participate in a field program aboard a French research vessel. He will collaborate on the study of the collected underway geophysical data and rock samples. The expedition is scheduled for September, 2006 aboard the Marion Dufresnes.  &lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
